entries.title: 'Secondhand pessimism': Chamber president blasts government in annual speech
entries.description: The head of the United States Chamber of Commerce used her annual speech on the state of U.S. business to tear into government gridlock and overregulation, saying that businesses were becoming pessimistic about their own prospects because of politics.

entries.title: Texas Congressman files three articles of impeachment against Mayorkas
entries.description: (The Center Square) – U.S. Rep. Pat Fallon, a Republican from northeast Texas, filed articles of impeachment against Department of Homeland Security Secretary Alejandro Mayorkas.
